{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-jsx","path":"/blog/my-third-blog/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"name":"Changi Im","title":"Hi, I'm Changi","description":"Studying Vision & Image Across the World","about":"Welcome to the Changi website! \n    Currently, I work as an engineer at Samsung Electronics, System LSI in South Korea. My research interests are focused on practical image processing that can address various problems worldwide.\n    I enjoy sharing ideas with others, particularly through brainstorming sessions. It's truly enjoyable to exchange random thoughts and develop them into innovative ideas.\n    Thank you for visiting my website again. Below, you'll find more information about me!","author":"","contact":"mailto:imchmcgi250@gmail.com","github":"https://www.github.com/Changi-Im","linkedin":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/changi-im-aa312a215/"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"fe5492b7-4c9e-57a4-a829-03c52e8955eb","excerpt":"We designed new appearance of our smart pet robot in the last post. Also, we made her face using 3.5 inch raspberry pi LCD display. \nHowever, the raspberry pi…","html":"<p>We designed new appearance of our smart pet robot in the last post. Also, we made her face using 3.5 inch raspberry pi LCD display.\nHowever, the raspberry pi display had low fps so her blinking was quite unnatural. In order to solve this problem, we changed some configurations in the raspberry pi. Refer to this video and you could find out how to make it. <cite><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cQvC-UI2vQY\">video</a></cite> </p>\n<center>\n<video width = \"50%\" muted autoplay controls>\n    <source src=\"/95b471b98274568a3ca61cadc8468465/disp_better.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n</video>\n</center>  \n<p>As you can see the above video, now it has more higher fps. The next step is making a 3d drawing file according to our new design sketch. The picture below is a 3d image using inventor program.  </p>\n<center>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; margin: 0 0 30px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/034c30280f3366f1154e5f312bc0bbb9/0b5b1/3D_design.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 99.32432432432432%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"3D_design\" title=\"3D_design\" src=\"/static/034c30280f3366f1154e5f312bc0bbb9/fcda8/3D_design.png\" srcset=\"/static/034c30280f3366f1154e5f312bc0bbb9/12f09/3D_design.png 148w,\n/static/034c30280f3366f1154e5f312bc0bbb9/e4a3f/3D_design.png 295w,\n/static/034c30280f3366f1154e5f312bc0bbb9/fcda8/3D_design.png 590w,\n/static/034c30280f3366f1154e5f312bc0bbb9/0b5b1/3D_design.png 593w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 512px; margin: 0 0 30px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/39ead2c4af6208a5bc5a5f32633ff77a/36dd4/printed_3D.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"printed_3D\" title=\"printed_3D\" src=\"/static/39ead2c4af6208a5bc5a5f32633ff77a/36dd4/printed_3D.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/39ead2c4af6208a5bc5a5f32633ff77a/a80bd/printed_3D.jpg 148w,\n/static/39ead2c4af6208a5bc5a5f32633ff77a/1c91a/printed_3D.jpg 295w,\n/static/39ead2c4af6208a5bc5a5f32633ff77a/36dd4/printed_3D.jpg 512w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 512px; margin: 0 0 30px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/488d9851454645ae7b5b272ccb81b21f/36dd4/painted_3D.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"painted_3D\" title=\"painted_3D\" src=\"/static/488d9851454645ae7b5b272ccb81b21f/36dd4/painted_3D.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/488d9851454645ae7b5b272ccb81b21f/a80bd/painted_3D.jpg 148w,\n/static/488d9851454645ae7b5b272ccb81b21f/1c91a/painted_3D.jpg 295w,\n/static/488d9851454645ae7b5b272ccb81b21f/36dd4/painted_3D.jpg 512w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n</center>  \n<p>We printed her on 3D printer and dyed. It was such a boring time. Because printing and dyeing took a lot of time. Meanwile, as time went on, We could make her.<br>\nShe is really cute. I couldn’t stop looking at her. Let’s look at our adorable smart robot.  </p>\n<center>\n<video width = \"50%\" muted autoplay controls>\n    <source src=\"/433ff44ae084c749ac3645af9631917f/playing.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n</video>\n </center>  \n<p>She wags her tail when we smile! This is amazing right.\nWe submitted to hanium contest and awaiting the result right now. Hopefully we can win the prize!</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Smart Pet Robot[2]","date":"October 09, 2022","description":"Robot expression"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/my-third-blog/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/my-second-blog/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Smart Pet Robot[1]"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/my-fourth-blog/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Model Compression"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["63159454"]}